Lambda

Without innovation:


p <- ggplot(saa12finalnoinnov, aes(x = msg_lambda)) + geom_density(fill = "red")
p + facet_grid(learning_rate ~ size_trait_space, scale = "free_y")

And with innovation:


p <- ggplot(saa12finalinnov, aes(x = msg_lambda)) + geom_density(fill = "red")
p + facet_grid(learning_rate ~ size_trait_space, scale = "free_y")
